public int blackjack(int a, int b)                                                                  public int blackjack(int a, int b)                                                                  
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    if(a > 21 && b > 21 )                                                                               if(a > 21 && b > 21 )                                                                           
        return 0;                                                                                           return 0;                                                                                   
    if(b > 21 && a < 21)                                                                                if(b > 21 && a < 21)                                                                            
        return a;                                                                                           return a;                                                                                   
    if(a>21 && b < 21)                                                                                  if(a>21 && b < 21)                                                                              
        return b;                                                                                           return b;                                                                                   
    else {                                                                                              else {                                                                                          
    	if(a > b)                                                                                          	if(a > b)                                                                                      
        	return a;                                                                                          	return a;                                                                                  
    	if (b > a)                                                                                         	if (b > a)                                                                                     
        	return a;                                                                                          	return b;                                                                                  
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    return 0;                                                                                           return 0;                                                                                       
}                                                                                                   }

public String zipZap(String str)                                                                    public String zipZap(String str)                                                                    
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
        StringBuilder newStr = new StringBuilder(str);                                                      StringBuilder newStr = new StringBuilder(str);                                              
    for (int i = 0; i<= str.length()-3; i++)                                                            for (int i = 0; i< str.length()-3; i++)                                                         
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
    	if (str.charAt(i) == 'z' && str.charAt(i+2) == 'p')                                                	if (str.charAt(i) == 'z' && str.charAt(i+2) == 'p')                                            
    	{                                                                                                  	{                                                                                              
        	newStr.deleteCharAt(i+1);                                                                          	newStr.deleteCharAt(i+1);                                                                  
    	}                                                                                                  	}                                                                                              
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    return newStr.toString();                                                                           return newStr.toString();                                                                       
}                                                                                                   }

public boolean evenlySpaced(int a, int b, int c)                                                    public boolean evenlySpaced(int a, int b, int c)                                                    
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    int biggest;                                                                                        int biggest;                                                                                    
    int middle = c;                                                                                     int middle = b;                                                                                 
    int lowest;                                                                                         int lowest;                                                                                     
	if (a - c < 0 && a - b < 0) {                                                                      	if (a - c < 0 && a - b < 0) {                                                                      
        lowest = a;                                                                                         lowest = a;                                                                                 
    } else {                                                                                            } else {                                                                                        
        if (b - c < 0 && b - a < 0) {                                                                       if (b - c < 0 && b - a < 0) {                                                               
            lowest = b;                                                                                         lowest = b;                                                                             
        }                                                                                                   }                                                                                           
        lowest = c;                                                                                         lowest = c;                                                                                 
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    if (a - c > 0 && a - b > 0) {                                                                       if (a - c > 0 && a - b > 0) {                                                                   
        biggest = a;                                                                                        biggest = a;                                                                                
    } else {                                                                                            } else {                                                                                        
        if (b - c > 0 && b - a > 0) {                                                                       if (b - c > 0 && b - a > 0) {                                                               
            biggest = b;                                                                                        biggest = b;                                                                            
        }                                                                                                   }                                                                                           
        biggest = c;                                                                                        biggest = c;                                                                                
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    int difference_medium_small = middle - lowest;                                                      int difference_medium_small = middle - lowest;                                                  
	int differennce_medium_large = biggest - middle;                                                   	int differennce_medium_large = biggest - middle;                                                   
	if (difference_medium_small == differennce_medium_large) {                                         	if (difference_medium_small == differennce_medium_large) {                                         
		return true;                                                                                      		return true;                                                                                      
	} else {                                                                                           	} else {                                                                                           
		return false;                                                                                     		return false;                                                                                     
}                                                                                                   }                                                                                                   
}                                                                                                   }

public boolean squirrelPlay(int temp, boolean isSummer)                                             public boolean squirrelPlay(int temp, boolean isSummer)                                             
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    if(temp <= 60)                                                                                      if(temp < 60)                                                                                   
        return false;                                                                                       return false;                                                                               
    temp += !isSummer ? 10 : 0;                                                                         temp += !isSummer ? 10 : 0;                                                                     
    if(temp <= 100)                                                                                     if(temp <= 100)                                                                                 
        return true;                                                                                        return true;                                                                                
    return false;                                                                                       return false;                                                                                   
}                                                                                                   }

        return b + c;                                                                                       return c;                                                                                   
    } else if (b == c) {                                                                                } else if (b == c) {

    } else if (a == c) {                                                                                } else if (a == c) {

        return a + b + c;                                                                                   return a + b + c;

public String getSandwich(String str)                                                               public String getSandwich(String str)                                                               
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    String returnStr = "";                                                                              String returnStr = "";                                                                          
    String tempStr = "";                                                                                String tempStr = "";                                                                            
    int startStr = 0;                                                                                   int startStr = 0;                                                                               
    int endStr = 0;                                                                                     int endStr = 0;                                                                                 
    boolean firstBread = false;                                                                         boolean firstBread = false;                                                                     
                                                                                                                                                                                                        
    if (str.length() > 10)                                                                              if (str.length() > 10)                                                                          
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
                                                                                                                                                                                                        
        for (int i = 0; i < str.length() - 4; i++)                                                          for (int i = 0; i < str.length() - 4; i++)                                                  
        {                                                                                                   {                                                                                           
            tempStr = str.substring(i, i + 4);                                                                  tempStr = str.substring(i, i + 5);                                                      
            if (tempStr.equals("bread") && firstBread ==   					true)                                           if (tempStr.equals("bread") && firstBread ==   					true)                               
            {                                                                                                   {                                                                                       
                endStr = i;                                                                                         endStr = i;                                                                         
            }                                                                                                   }                                                                                       
            if (tempStr.equals("bread") && firstBread == 					false)                                            if (tempStr.equals("bread") && firstBread == 					false)                                
            {                                                                                                   {                                                                                       
                startStr = i + 5;                                                                                   startStr = i + 5;                                                                   
                firstBread = true;                                                                                  firstBread = true;                                                                  
            }                                                                                                   }                                                                                       
        }                                                                                                   }                                                                                           
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
                                                                                                                                                                                                        
    returnStr = str.substring(startStr, endStr);                                                        returnStr = str.substring(startStr, endStr);                                                    
    return returnStr;                                                                                   return returnStr;                                                                               
}                                                                                                   }

public String getSandwich(String str)                                                               public String getSandwich(String str)                                                               
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    int first = -1;                                                                                     int first = -1;                                                                                 
    int last = -1;                                                                                      int last = -1;                                                                                  
    for (int i = 0 ; i < str.length() - 5 ; i++)                                                                                                                                                        
    {                                                                                                   for(int i = 0; i < str.length() - 5; i++) {                                                     
         if(str.substring(i, i + 5).equals("bread"))                                                        if(str.substring(i, i + 5).equals("bread")) {                                               
         {                                                                                                      first = i;                                                                              
            first = i;                                                                                          break;                                                                                  
            break;                                                                                          }                                                                                           
         }                                                                                              }                                                                                               
    }                                                                                                                                                                                                   
    for (int i = 0 ; i < str.length() - 5 ; i++)                                                        for(int i = str.length() - 5; i >= 0; i--) {                                                    
    {                                                                                                       if(str.substring(i, i + 5).equals("bread")) {                                               
     	if(str.substring(i, i + 5).equals("bread"))                                                               last = i;                                                                               
        {                                                                                                       break;                                                                                  
            last = i;                                                                                       }                                                                                           
            break;                                                                                      }                                                                                               
        }                                                                                                                                                                                               
    }                                                                                                   if(first != -1 && last != -1 && first != last)                                                  
    if (first != -1 && last != -1 && first != last)                                                         return str.substring(first + 5, last);                                                      
    {                                                                                                                                                                                                   
        return str.substring(first + 5, last);                                                          return "";                                                                                      
    }                                                                                               }                                                                                                   
    else                                                                                                                                                                                                
    {                                                                                                                                                                                                   
    return "";                                                                                                                                                                                          
    }                                                                                                                                                                                                   
}

public int loneSum(int a, int b, int c)                                                             public int loneSum(int a, int b, int c)                                                             
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    int numA = a;                                                                                       int numA = a;                                                                                   
    int numB = b;                                                                                       int numB = b;                                                                                   
    int numC = c;                                                                                       int numC = c;                                                                                   
    if (numA == numB)                                                                                   if (numA == numB && numA == numC)                                                               
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        return numA + numC;                                                                                 return 0;                                                                                   
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    if (numA == numC)                                                                                   if (numA == numB)                                                                               
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        return numA + numB;                                                                                 return numC;                                                                                
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    if (numB == numC)                                                                                   if (numA == numC)                                                                               
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        return numA + numB;                                                                                 return numB;                                                                                
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    return numA + numB + numC;                                                                          if (numB == numC)                                                                               
}                                                                                                       {                                                                                               
                                                                                                            return numA;                                                                                
                                                                                                        }                                                                                               
                                                                                                        return numA + numB + numC;                                                                      
                                                                                                    }

    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        return a;                                                                                           return 0;                                                                                   
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else if (a == b)                                                                                    else if (a == b)                                                                                
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        return (a+c);                                                                                       return (c);                                                                                 
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else if (a == c)                                                                                    else if (a == c)                                                                                
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        return (a+b);                                                                                       return (b);                                                                                 
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else if (b == c)                                                                                    else if (b == c)                                                                                
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        return (a+b);                                                                                       return (a);                                                                                 
    }                                                                                                   }

public int blackjack(int a, int b)                                                                  public int blackjack(int a, int b)                                                                  
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    int aChecker = 21 - a;                                                                              int aChecker = 21 - a;                                                                          
    int bChecker = 21 - b;                                                                              int bChecker = 21 - b;                                                                          
    int answer = 0;                                                                                     int answer = 0;                                                                                 
    if (aChecker < bChecker)                                                                            if (aChecker < bChecker)                                                                        
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        answer = a;                                                                                         answer = a;                                                                                 
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    if (aChecker > bChecker)                                                                            if (aChecker > bChecker)                                                                        
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        answer = b;                                                                                         answer = b;                                                                                 
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    if (aChecker < 0 && bChecker < 0)                                                                   if (aChecker < 0 && bChecker >= 0)                                                              
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        answer = 0;                                                                                         answer = b;                                                                                 
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    return answer;                                                                                      if (aChecker >= 0 && bChecker < 0)                                                              
}                                                                                                       {                                                                                               
                                                                                                            answer = a;                                                                                 
                                                                                                        }                                                                                               
                                                                                                        if (aChecker < 0 && bChecker < 0)                                                               
                                                                                                        {                                                                                               
                                                                                                            answer = 0;                                                                                 
                                                                                                        }                                                                                               
                                                                                                        return answer;                                                                                  
                                                                                                    }

   		if (a < b)                                                                                        		if (a < b)

public boolean answerCell(boolean isMorning, boolean isMom, boolean isAsleep)                       public boolean answerCell(boolean isMorning, boolean isMom, boolean isAsleep)                       
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    if (isMorning)                                                                                      if (isMorning)                                                                                  
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        if (isMom && isAsleep)                                                                              if (isMom && isAsleep)                                                                      
        {                                                                                                   {                                                                                           
            return true;                                                                                        return false;                                                                           
        }                                                                                                   }                                                                                           
        else if (isMom && !isAsleep)                                                                        else if (isMom && !isAsleep)                                                                
        {                                                                                                   {                                                                                           
            return true;                                                                                        return true;                                                                            
        }                                                                                                   }                                                                                           
        else if (!isMom && isAsleep)                                                                        else if (!isMom && isAsleep)                                                                
        {                                                                                                   {                                                                                           
            return false;                                                                                       return false;                                                                           
        }                                                                                                   }                                                                                           
        else if (!isMom && !isAsleep)                                                                       else if (!isMom && !isAsleep)                                                               
        {                                                                                                   {                                                                                           
            return false;                                                                                       return false;                                                                           
        }                                                                                                   }                                                                                           
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    if (!isMorning)                                                                                     if (!isMorning)                                                                                 
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        if (isAsleep)                                                                                       if (isAsleep)                                                                               
        {                                                                                                   {                                                                                           
            return false;                                                                                       return false;                                                                           
        }                                                                                                   }                                                                                           
        else                                                                                                else                                                                                        
        {                                                                                                   {                                                                                           
            return true;                                                                                        return true;                                                                            
        }                                                                                                   }                                                                                           
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    return false;                                                                                       return false;                                                                                   
}                                                                                                   }

public boolean answerCell(boolean isMorning, boolean isMom, boolean isAsleep)                       public boolean answerCell(boolean isMorning, boolean isMom, boolean isAsleep)

        t=true;                                                                                             t=false;                                                                                    
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else if (isAsleep==true)                                                                            else if (isMorning==true && isMom==true)                                                        
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        t=false;                                                                                            t=true;                                                                                     
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else if (isMorning==true && isMom!=true)                                                                                                                                                            
    {                                                                                                   else if (isMorning==true && isMom!=true)                                                        
        t=false;                                                                                        {                                                                                               
    }                                                                                                       t=false;                                                                                    
                                                                                                        }                                                                                               
    else                                                                                                                                                                                                
    {                                                                                                   else                                                                                            
    	t=true;                                                                                            {                                                                                               
    }                                                                                                   	t=true;                                                                                        
    return t;                                                                                           }                                                                                               
}                                                                                                       return t;                                                                                       
                                                                                                    }

public int sortaSum(int a, int b)                                                                   public int sortaSum(int a, int b)                                                                   
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    int sum;                                                                                            int sum;                                                                                        
    int add = a + b;                                                                                    int add = a + b;                                                                                
    if (add >= 10 || add <= 19)                                                                         if (add >= 10 && add <= 19)                                                                     
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        sum = 20;                                                                                           sum = 20;                                                                                   
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else                                                                                                else                                                                                            
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        sum = add;                                                                                          sum = add;                                                                                  
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    return sum;                                                                                         return sum;                                                                                     
}                                                                                                   }

    }                                                                                                   }

public int loneSum(int a, int b, int c)                                                             public int loneSum(int a, int b, int c)                                                             
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    int sum = 0;                                                                                        int sum = 0;                                                                                    
    if (a != b && a != c)                                                                               if (a != b && a != c && b != c)                                                                 
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        sum = a + b + c;                                                                                    sum = a + b + c;                                                                            
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else if (a == b && a == c)                                                                          else if (a == b && a == c)                                                                      
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        sum = 0;                                                                                            sum = 0;                                                                                    
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else if (a == b)                                                                                    else if (a == b)                                                                                
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        sum = c;                                                                                            sum = c;                                                                                    
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else if (a == c)                                                                                    else if (a == c)                                                                                
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        sum = b;                                                                                            sum = b;                                                                                    
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else if (b == c)                                                                                    else if (b == c)                                                                                
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        sum = a;                                                                                            sum = a;                                                                                    
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
                                                                                                                                                                                                        
    return sum;                                                                                         return sum;                                                                                     
}                                                                                                   }

public String getSandwich(String str)                                                               public String getSandwich(String str)                                                               
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    int length = str.length();                                                                          int length = str.length();                                                                      
    boolean a = true;                                                                                   boolean a = true;                                                                               
    int first = 0;                                                                                      int first = 0;                                                                                  
    int last = 0;                                                                                       int last = 0;                                                                                   
    if	(length <= 10)                                                                                   if	(length <= 10)                                                                               
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        return "";                                                                                          return "";                                                                                  
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    for (int i = 0; i < length - 5; i++)                                                                for (int i = 0; i < length - 5; i++)                                                            
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        if	(str.substring(i, i + 4).equals("bread"))                                                        if	(str.substring(i, i + 5).equals("bread"))                                                
        {                                                                                                   {                                                                                           
            first = i;                                                                                          first = i;                                                                              
            break;                                                                                              break;                                                                                  
        }                                                                                                   }                                                                                           
        else                                                                                                else                                                                                        
        {                                                                                                   {                                                                                           
        	a = false;                                                                                         	a = false;                                                                                 
        }                                                                                                   }                                                                                           
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    for	(int i = first; i < length - 5; i++)                                                            for	(int i = first; i < length - 5; i++)                                                        
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        if (str.substring(i, i + 4).equals("bread"))                                                        if (str.substring(i, i + 5).equals("bread"))                                                
        {                                                                                                   {                                                                                           
            last = i;                                                                                           last = i;                                                                               
            break;                                                                                              break;                                                                                  
        }                                                                                                   }                                                                                           
        else                                                                                                else                                                                                        
        {                                                                                                   {                                                                                           
            a = false;                                                                                          a = false;                                                                              
        }                                                                                                   }                                                                                           
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    if	(a == true)                                                                                      if	(a == true)                                                                                  
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        return (str.substring(first+5, last-1));                                                            return (str.substring(first+5, last-1));                                                    
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else                                                                                                else                                                                                            
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        return "";                                                                                          return "";                                                                                  
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
}                                                                                                   }

public String zipZap(String str)                                                                    public String zipZap(String str)                                                                    
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    String newStr = "";                                                                                 String newStr = str;                                                                            
    int length = str.length() - 1;                                                                      int length = str.length() - 1;                                                                  
    for (int i = length; i >= 2; i--)                                                                   for (int i = length; i >= 2; i--)                                                               
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        if (str.charAt(i) == 'p' && str.charAt(i-2) == 'z')                                                 if (str.charAt(i) == 'p' && str.charAt(i-2) == 'z')                                         
        {                                                                                                   {                                                                                           
            newStr = str.substring(0, i-1) + str.substring(i);                                                  newStr = str.substring(0, i-1) + str.substring(i);                                      
        }                                                                                                   }                                                                                           
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    return newStr;                                                                                      return newStr;                                                                                  
}                                                                                                   }

public boolean evenlySpaced(int a, int b, int c)                                                    public boolean evenlySpaced(int a, int b, int c)                                                    
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    int biggest;                                                                                        int biggest;                                                                                    
    int middle = c;                                                                                     int middle = b;                                                                                 
    int lowest;                                                                                         int lowest;                                                                                     
	if (a - c < 0 && a - b < 0) {                                                                      	if (a - c < 0 && a - b < 0) {                                                                      
        lowest = a;                                                                                         lowest = a;                                                                                 
    } else {                                                                                            } else {                                                                                        
        if (b - c < 0 && b - a < 0) {                                                                       if (b - c < 0 && b - a < 0) {                                                               
            lowest = b;                                                                                         lowest = b;                                                                             
        }                                                                                                   }                                                                                           
        lowest = c;                                                                                         lowest = c;                                                                                 
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    if (a - c > 0 && a - b > 0) {                                                                       if (a - c > 0 && a - b > 0) {                                                                   
        biggest = a;                                                                                        biggest = a;                                                                                
    } else {                                                                                            } else {                                                                                        
        if (b - c > 0 && b - a > 0) {                                                                       if (b - c > 0 && b - a > 0) {                                                               
            biggest = b;                                                                                        biggest = b;                                                                            
        }                                                                                                   }                                                                                           
        biggest = c;                                                                                        biggest = c;                                                                                
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    int difference_medium_small = middle - lowest;                                                      int difference_medium_small = middle - lowest;                                                  
	int differennce_medium_large = biggest - middle;                                                   	int differennce_medium_large = biggest - middle;                                                   
	if (difference_medium_small == differennce_medium_large) {                                         	if (difference_medium_small == differennce_medium_large) {                                         
		return true;                                                                                      		return true;                                                                                      
	} else {                                                                                           	} else {                                                                                           
		return false;                                                                                     		return false;                                                                                     
}                                                                                                   }                                                                                                   
}                                                                                                   }

        // do nothing                                                                                       // do nothing                                                                               
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else if (a == b)                                                                                    else if (a == b)

    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else if (a == c)                                                                                    else if (a == c)                                                                                
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        sum = a;                                                                                            sum = b;
