public int blackjack(int a, int b)                                                                  public int blackjack(int a, int b)                                                                  
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    if (a <= 21 && b <= 21)                                                                             if (a <= 21 && b <= 21)                                                                         
   		if (a < b)                                                                                        		if (a < b)                                                                                     
            return b;                                                                                           return b;                                                                               
    	else if (b < a)                                                                                    	else if (b < a)                                                                                
            return a;                                                                                           return a;                                                                               
    return 0;                                                                                           if (a > 21 && b <= 21)                                                                          
}                                                                                                           return b;                                                                                   
                                                                                                        if (b > 21 && a <= 21)                                                                          
                                                                                                            return a;                                                                                   
                                                                                                        return 0;                                                                                       
                                                                                                    }                                                                                                   
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
public int blackjack(int a, int b)                                                                  public int blackjack(int a, int b)                                                                  
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    if (a > 21 && b > 21) {                                                                           if (a > 21 && b > 21) {                                                                           
        return 0;                                                                                         return 0;                                                                                     
    }else if (a > 21) {                                                                               }else if (a > 21) {                                                                               
        return a;                                                                                         return b;                                                                                     
    }                                                                                                 } else if (b > 21) {                                                                              
                                                                                                          return a;                                                                                     
    int sumA = 21 - a;                                                                                }                                                                                                 
    int sumB = 21 - b;                                                                                int sumA = 21 - a;                                                                                
                                                                                                      int sumB = 21 - b;                                                                                
    if (sumA > sumB) {                                                                                if (sumA > sumB) {                                                                                
        return b;                                                                                         return b;                                                                                     
    } else {                                                                                          } else {                                                                                          
        return a;                                                                                         return a;                                                                                     
    }                                                                                                 }                                                                                                 
}                                                                                                   }

public String zipZap(String str)                                                                    public String zipZap(String str)                                                                    
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    for(int i = 2; i < str.length(); i++)                                                               for(int i = 2; i < str.length(); i++)                                                           
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        if(str.charAt(i) == 'p' && str.charAt(i-2) == 'z')                                                  if(str.charAt(i) == 'p' && str.charAt(i-2) == 'z')                                          
        {                                                                                                   {                                                                                           
            str = str.substring(0, i-2) + str.substring(i);                                                     str = str.substring(0, i-1) + str.substring(i);                                         
        }                                                                                                   }                                                                                           
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
	return str;                                                                                        	return str;                                                                                        
}                                                                                                   }

public String zipZap(String str)                                                                    public String zipZap(String str)                                                                    
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    for (int i = 0; i < str.length()-2; i++)                                                            for (int i = 0; i < str.length()-2; i++)                                                        
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        if (str.charAt(i) == 'z' && str.charAt(i+2) == 'p')                                                 if (str.charAt(i) == 'z' && str.charAt(i+2) == 'p')                                         
        {                                                                                                   {                                                                                           
            str = str.substring(0, i) + str.substring(i+2);                                                     String newStr = str.substring(0, i+1) + str.substring(i+2);                             
        }                                                                                                       str = newStr;                                                                           
    }                                                                                                       }                                                                                           
    return str;                                                                                         }                                                                                               
}                                                                                                       return str;                                                                                     
                                                                                                    }                                                                                                   
***********************************************************************************************************************


public int loneSum(int a, int b, int c)                                                             public int loneSum(int a, int b, int c)                                                             
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    int sum;                                                                                            if (a == b && a == c)                                                                           
                                                                                                        {                                                                                               
    if (a != b && a != c)                                                                                   return 0;                                                                                   
    {                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
        sum = a + b + c;                                                                                else if (a == b)                                                                                
    }                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
    else if (b == c && a != c)                                                                              return c;                                                                                   
    {                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
        sum = a;                                                                                        else if (b == c)                                                                                
    }                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
    else if (a == c && b != c)                                                                              return a;                                                                                   
    {                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
        sum = b;                                                                                        else if (a == c)                                                                                
    }                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
    else if (a == b && c != b)                                                                              return b;                                                                                   
    {                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
        sum = c;                                                                                        else                                                                                            
    }                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
    else                                                                                                    return a + b + c;                                                                           
    {                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
        sum = 0;                                                                                    }                                                                                                   
    }                                                                                                                                                                                                   
                                                                                                                                                                                                        
    return sum;                                                                                                                                                                                         
}

{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    if (isBirthday)                                                                                     if (!isBirthday)                                                                                
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        if (speed <= 60)                                                                                    if (speed <= 60)                                                                            
        {                                                                                                   {                                                                                           
            return 0;                                                                                           return 0;                                                                               
        }                                                                                                   }                                                                                           
        else if (speed <= 80 && speed >= 61)                                                                else if (speed <= 80 && speed >= 61)                                                        
        {                                                                                                   {                                                                                           
            return 1;                                                                                           return 1;                                                                               
        }                                                                                                   }                                                                                           
        else                                                                                                else                                                                                        
        {                                                                                                   {                                                                                           
            return 2;                                                                                           return 2;                                                                               
        }                                                                                                   }                                                                                           
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else                                                                                                else                                                                                            
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        if (speed <= 65)                                                                                    if (speed <= 65)                                                                            
        {                                                                                                   {                                                                                           
            return 0;                                                                                           return 0;                                                                               
        }                                                                                                   }                                                                                           
        else if (speed <= 85 && speed >= 66)                                                                else if (speed <= 85 && speed >= 66)                                                        
        {                                                                                                   {

        }                                                                                                   }

        {                                                                                                   {                                                                                           
            return 2;                                                                                           return 2;

    String endb = bb.substring(lenb-lena, lenb);                                                        {

    if(enda.equals(bb) || endb.equals(aa))                                                                  if(enda.equals(bb))                                                                         
        return true;                                                                                        {                                                                                           
    return false;                                                                                               return true;                                                                            
                                                                                                            }

        return c;                                                                                           return 0;                                                                                   
    else if (a == c)                                                                                    else if (a == b)                                                                                
        return b;                                                                                           return c;                                                                                   
    else if (b == a)                                                                                    else if (a == c)                                                                                
        return c;                                                                                           return b;                                                                                   
    else if (b == c)                                                                                    else if (b == a)                                                                                
        return a;                                                                                           return c;                                                                                   
    else if (c == a)                                                                                    else if (b == c)                                                                                
        return b;                                                                                           return a;                                                                                   
    else if (c == b)                                                                                    else if (c == a)                                                                                
        return a;                                                                                           return b;                                                                                   
    else if (a==b && b==c)                                                                              else if (c == b)                                                                                
        return 0;                                                                                           return a;

}                                                                                                               return b;

    return b;                                                                                               return b;                                                                                   
    else                                                                                                else if ( b> 21)

public int blackjack(int a, int b)                                                                  public int blackjack(int a, int b)                                                                  
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    if (a > 21 && b > 21)                                                                               if (a > 21 && b > 21)                                                                           
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
    return 0;                                                                                           return 0;                                                                                       
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else if ( a <= 21 && a > b )                                                                        else if ( a <= 21 && a > b || a <= 21 && b > 21 )                                               
        return a;                                                                                           return a;                                                                                   
    else if ( b <= 21 && a < b )                                                                        else if ( b <= 21 && a < b || b <= 21 && a> 21)                                                 
        return b;                                                                                           return b;                                                                                   
    return 0;                                                                                       return 0;// ???                                                                                     
}                                                                                                   }

public String zipZap(String str)                                                                    public String zipZap(String str)                                                                    
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    StringBuilder newStr = new StringBuilder(str);                                                      StringBuilder newStr = new StringBuilder(str);                                                  
    for (int i = 0; i< str.length()-3; i++)                                                             for (int i = 0; i< str.length()-2; i++)                                                         
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
    	if (str.charAt(i) == 'z' && str.charAt(i+2) == 'p')                                                	if (str.charAt(i) == 'z' && str.charAt(i+2) == 'p')                                            
    	{                                                                                                  	{                                                                                              
        	newStr.deleteCharAt(i+1);                                                                          	newStr.deleteCharAt(i+1);                                                                  
    	}                                                                                                  	}                                                                                              
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    return newStr.toString();                                                                           return newStr.toString();                                                                       
}                                                                                                   }

     	return a + b + c;                                                                                  	return a + b + c;

		return b;                                                                                         		return b;                                                                                         
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else if (a != c && a == b)                                                                          else if (a != c && a == b)                                                                      
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        return c;                                                                                           return c;                                                                                   
    }                                                                                                   }

     	return a;                                                                                          	return a;                                                                                     
    }                                                                                                   }

    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        return (c);                                                                                         return 0;                                                                                   
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else if (a == c)                                                                                    else if (a == b)                                                                                
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        return (b);                                                                                         return (c);                                                                                 
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else if (b == c)                                                                                    else if (a == c)                                                                                
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        return (a);                                                                                         return (b);                                                                                 
    }                                                                                                   }

        return 0;                                                                                           return (a);

    }                                                                                                   }

public int loneSum(int a, int b, int c)                                                             public int loneSum(int a, int b, int c)                                                             
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    int sum = 0;                                                                                        int sum = 0;                                                                                    
    if (a != b && b!= c)                                                                                if (a == b && b != c)                                                                           
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
    	sum = a + b + c;                                                                                   	sum = c;                                                                                       
        return sum;                                                                                         return sum;                                                                                 
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else if (a == b && b != c)                                                                          else if (a != b && b == c)                                                                      
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
    	sum = c;                                                                                           	sum = a;                                                                                       
        return sum;                                                                                         return sum;                                                                                 
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else if (a != b && b == c)                                                                          else if (a == c && b != c)                                                                      
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
    	sum = a;                                                                                           	sum = b;                                                                                       
        return sum;                                                                                         return sum;                                                                                 
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else if (a == c && b != c)                                                                          else if (a != b && b!= c)                                                                       
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
    	sum = b;                                                                                           	sum = a + b + c;                                                                               
        return sum;                                                                                         return sum;                                                                                 
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else                                                                                                else                                                                                            
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
    	sum = 0;                                                                                           	sum = 0;                                                                                       
        return sum;                                                                                         return sum;                                                                                 
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
}                                                                                                   }

    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        return a;                                                                                           return c;                                                                                   
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else if (a==c)                                                                                      else if (b==c)

public int blackjack(int a, int b)                                                                  public int blackjack(int a, int b)                                                                  
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    int bj=0;                                                                                           int bj=0;                                                                                       
                                                                                                                                                                                                        
    int da=21-a;                                                                                        int da=21-a;                                                                                    
    int db=21-b;                                                                                        int db=21-b;                                                                                    
    if(da>db)                                                                                           if(da>db)                                                                                       
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        bj=b;                                                                                               bj=b;                                                                                       
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    if(db>da)                                                                                           if(db>da)                                                                                       
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        bj=a;                                                                                               bj=a;                                                                                       
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
                                                                                                                                                                                                        
    if((a>21)&&(b>21))                                                                                  if((a>21)&&(b>21))                                                                              
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        bj=0;                                                                                               bj=0;                                                                                       
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    return bj;                                                                                          if((a>21)&&(b<21))                                                                              
                                                                                                        {                                                                                               
}                                                                                                           bj=b;                                                                                       
                                                                                                        }                                                                                               
                                                                                                        if((b>21)&&(a<21))                                                                              
                                                                                                        {                                                                                               
                                                                                                            bj=a;                                                                                       
                                                                                                        }                                                                                               
                                                                                                        return bj;                                                                                      
                                                                                                                                                                                                        
                                                                                                    }                                                                                                   
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
public int blackjack(int a, int b)                                                                  public int blackjack(int a, int b)                                                                  
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    if (a > 21 && b > 21)                                                                               if (a > 21 && b > 21)                                                                           
        return 0;                                                                                           return 0;                                                                                   
    else if (a - b > 0)                                                                                 else if (a > 21 && b <= 21)                                                                     
        return a;                                                                                           return b;                                                                                   
    else if (b - a > 0)                                                                                 else if (a <= 21 && b > 21)                                                                     
        return b;                                                                                           return a;                                                                                   
    else                                                                                                else if (a - b > 0)                                                                             
        return 0;                                                                                           return a;                                                                                   
}                                                                                                       else if (b - a > 0)                                                                             
                                                                                                            return b;                                                                                   
                                                                                                        else                                                                                            
                                                                                                            return 0;                                                                                   
                                                                                                    }

public String getSandwich(String str)                                                               public String getSandwich(String str)                                                               
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    int length = str.length();                                                                          int length = str.length();                                                                      
    boolean a = true;                                                                                   boolean a = true;                                                                               
    int first = 0;                                                                                      int first = 0;                                                                                  
    int last = 0;                                                                                       int last = 0;                                                                                   
    if	(length <= 10)                                                                                   if	(length <= 10)                                                                               
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        return "";                                                                                          return "";                                                                                  
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    for (int i = 0; i < length - 5; i++)                                                                for (int i = 0; i < length - 5; i++)                                                            
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        if	(str.substring(i, i + 4).equals("bread"))                                                        if	(str.substring(i, i + 5).equals("bread"))                                                
        {                                                                                                   {                                                                                           
            first = i;                                                                                          first = i;                                                                              
            break;                                                                                              break;                                                                                  
        }                                                                                                   }                                                                                           
        else                                                                                                else                                                                                        
        {                                                                                                   {                                                                                           
        	a = false;                                                                                         	a = false;                                                                                 
        }                                                                                                   }                                                                                           
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    for	(int i = first; i < length - 5; i++)                                                            for	(int i = first; i < length - 5; i++)                                                        
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        if (str.substring(i, i + 4).equals("bread"))                                                        if (str.substring(i, i + 5).equals("bread"))                                                
        {                                                                                                   {                                                                                           
            last = i;                                                                                           last = i;                                                                               
            break;                                                                                              break;                                                                                  
        }                                                                                                   }                                                                                           
        else                                                                                                else                                                                                        
        {                                                                                                   {                                                                                           
            a = false;                                                                                          a = false;                                                                              
        }                                                                                                   }                                                                                           
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    if	(a == true)                                                                                      if	(a == true)                                                                                  
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        return (str.substring(first+5, last-1));                                                            return (str.substring(first+5, last-1));                                                    
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else                                                                                                else                                                                                            
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        return "";                                                                                          return "";                                                                                  
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
}                                                                                                   }

public int luckySum(int a, int b, int c)                                                            public int luckySum(int a, int b, int c)                                                            
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    int s1=a+b+c;                                                                                       int s1=a+b+c;                                                                                   
    int s2=a+b;                                                                                         int s2=a+b;

    }                                                                                                   }

        return c;                                                                                           return 0;                                                                                   
    else if (a == c)                                                                                	else if (a == b)                                                                                   
        return b;                                                                                           return c;                                                                                   
    else if (b == c)                                                                                    else if (a == c)                                                                                
        return a;                                                                                           return b;                                                                                   
    else                                                                                                else if (b == c)                                                                                
        return a + b + c;                                                                                   return a;

public int loneSum(int a, int b, int c)                                                             public int loneSum(int a, int b, int c)                                                             
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    int sum = 0;                                                                                        int sum = 0;                                                                                    
    if (a != b && b!= c)                                                                                if (a == b && b != c)                                                                           
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
    	sum = a + b + c;                                                                                   	sum = c;                                                                                       
        return sum;                                                                                         return sum;                                                                                 
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else if (a == b && b != c)                                                                          else if (a != b && b == c)                                                                      
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
    	sum = c;                                                                                           	sum = a;                                                                                       
        return sum;                                                                                         return sum;                                                                                 
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else if (a != b && b == c)                                                                          else if (a == c && b != c)                                                                      
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
    	sum = a;                                                                                           	sum = b;                                                                                       
        return sum;                                                                                         return sum;                                                                                 
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else if (a == c && b != c)                                                                          else if (a != b && b!= c)                                                                       
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
    	sum = b;                                                                                           	sum = a + b + c;                                                                               
        return sum;                                                                                         return sum;                                                                                 
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else                                                                                                else                                                                                            
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
    	sum = 0;                                                                                           	sum = 0;                                                                                       
        return sum;                                                                                         return sum;                                                                                 
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
}                                                                                                   }

public boolean evenlySpaced(int a, int b, int c)                                                    public boolean evenlySpaced(int a, int b, int c)                                                    
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    if (a != b && b != c && a != c)                                                                     if ((a != b && b != c && a != c) || (a == b && b == c))                                         
        return ((Math.abs(a - b) == Math.abs(b - c))                                                        return ((Math.abs(a - b) == Math.abs(b - c))                                                
                || (Math.abs(b - a) == 	Math.abs(a - c))                                                            || (Math.abs(b - a) == 	Math.abs(a - c))                                            
                || (Math.abs(a - c) == Math.abs(c - b)));                                                           || (Math.abs(a - c) == Math.abs(c - b)));                                           
    else                                                                                                else                                                                                            
        return false;                                                                                       return false;                                                                               
}                                                                                                   }

    {                                                                                                   {

    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        result = true;                                                                                      result = true;                                                                              
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else if (Math.abs(c - a) == Math.abs(b - c))                                                        else if (Math.abs(a - b) == Math.abs(c - a))                                                    
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        result = true;                                                                                      result = true;                                                                              
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else                                                                                                else if (Math.abs(c - a) == Math.abs(b - c))

        result = false;                                                                                     result = true;                                                                              
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
                                                                                                        else                                                                                            
    return result;                                                                                      {

                                                                                                        return result;

    }                                                                                                   	    return 0;

        a = 0;                                                                                        	if(b == c)

        a = 0;                                                                                      }                                                                                                   
        b = 0;                                                                                                                                                                                          
        c = 0;                                                                                                                                                                                          
    }                                                                                                                                                                                                   
    return a + b + c;                                                                                                                                                                                   
}

public boolean isEverywhere(int[] nums, int val)                                                    public boolean isEverywhere(int[] nums, int val)                                                    
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    for (int i = 0; i < nums.length; i++)                                                               for (int i = 0; i < nums.length - 1; i++)                                                       
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        if ((nums[i] != val) && (nums[i + 1] != val))                                                       if ((nums[i] != val) && (nums[i + 1] != val))                                               
        {                                                                                                   {                                                                                           
            return false;                                                                                       return false;                                                                           
        }                                                                                                   }                                                                                           
                                                                                                                                                                                                        
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
     return true;                                                                                        return true;                                                                                   
}                                                                                                   }

public int loneSum(int a, int b, int c)                                                             public int loneSum(int a, int b, int c)
