    int loneSum = 0;                                                                                    int loneSum = 0;                                                                                
    if ( a == b && b == a )                                                                             if (c == b && a == b && b == a && b == c && a == c && c == a)                                   
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
    	loneSum = c;                                                                                       	loneSum = 0;                                                                                   
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else if ( b == c && c == b)                                                                         else if ( a == b && b == a )                                                                    
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
    	loneSum = a;                                                                                       	loneSum = c;                                                                                   
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else if ( a == c && c == a)                                                                         else if ( b == c && c == b)                                                                     
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
    	loneSum = b;                                                                                       	loneSum = a;                                                                                   
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else if (c == b && a == b && b == a && b == c && a == c && c == a)                                  else if ( a == c && c == a)                                                                     
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
    	loneSum = 0;                                                                                       	loneSum = b;                                                                                   
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else                                                                                                else                                                                                            
    {                                                                                                   {

    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    return loneSum;                                                                                     return loneSum;                                                                                 
}                                                                                                   }

public boolean endOther(String a, String b)                                                         public boolean endOther(String a, String b)                                                         
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    a.toLowerCase();                                                                                    a = a.toLowerCase();                                                                            
    b.toLowerCase();                                                                                    b = b.toLowerCase();                                                                            
                                                                                                                                                                                                        
    if (a.endsWith(b) || b.endsWith(a))                                                                 if (a.endsWith(b) || b.endsWith(a))                                                             
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        return true;                                                                                        return true;                                                                                
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else                                                                                                else                                                                                            
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        return false;                                                                                       return false;                                                                               
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
                                                                                                                                                                                                        
}                                                                                                   }

        return false;                                                                                       return false;                                                                               
}                                                                                                   }

public boolean xyBalance(String str)                                                                public boolean xyBalance(String str)                                                                
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
   int length = str.length() - 1;                                                                      int length = str.length() - 1;                                                                   
        int a = str.lastIndexOf("y");                                                                       int a = str.lastIndexOf("y");                                                               
    for (int i = length; i >= 0; i--)                                                                   for (int i = length; i >= 0; i--)                                                               
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
    	if(str.charAt(i) == 'y'){                                                                          	if(str.charAt(i) == 'y'){                                                                      
        return true;                                                                                        return true;                                                                                
        }                                                                                                   }                                                                                           
        else if (str.charAt(i) == 'x')                                                                      else if (str.charAt(i) == 'x')                                                              
        {                                                                                                   {                                                                                           
        return false;                                                                                       return false;                                                                               
        }                                                                                                   }                                                                                           
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    return false;                                                                                       return true;                                                                                    
}                                                                                                   }

public boolean xyBalance(String str)                                                                public boolean xyBalance(String str)                                                                
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    for (int i = str.length() - 1; i >= 0; i--)                                                         for (int i = str.length() - 1; i >= 0; i--)                                                     
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        if (str.charAt(i) == 'y')                                                                           if (str.charAt(i) == 'y')                                                                   
        {                                                                                                   {                                                                                           
            return true;                                                                                        return true;                                                                            
        }                                                                                                   }                                                                                           
        else if (str.charAt(i) == 'x')                                                                      else if (str.charAt(i) == 'x')                                                              
        {                                                                                                   {                                                                                           
            return false;                                                                                       return false;                                                                           
        }                                                                                                   }                                                                                           
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    return false;                                                                                       return true;                                                                                    
}                                                                                                   }

public int loneSum(int a, int b, int c)                                                             public int loneSum(int a, int b, int c)                                                             
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    if (a == b)                                                                                         if (a == b && a != c)                                                                           
        return c;                                                                                           return c;                                                                                   
    if (a == c)                                                                                         if (a == c && a != b)                                                                           
        return b;                                                                                           return b;                                                                                   
    if (b == c)                                                                                         if (b == c && b != a)                                                                           
        return a;                                                                                           return a;                                                                                   
    if (a == b && a == c)                                                                               if (a == b && a == c)                                                                           
        return 0;                                                                                           return 0;                                                                                   
    return (a + b + c);                                                                                 return (a + b + c);                                                                             
}                                                                                                   }

    else if (b - a > 0)                                                                                 else if (a <= 21 && b > 21)

                                                                                                            return 0;

public int sortaSum(int a, int b)                                                                   public int sortaSum(int a, int b)                                                                   
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
   int sum = a + b;                                                                                    int sum = a + b;                                                                                 
   if (sum >= 10 || sum <= 19)                                                                         if (sum >= 10 && sum <= 19)                                                                      
   {                                                                                                   {                                                                                                
   		return 20;                                                                                        		return 20;                                                                                     
   }                                                                                                   }                                                                                                
   else                                                                                                else                                                                                             
   {                                                                                                   {                                                                                                
   		return sum;                                                                                       		return sum;                                                                                    
   }                                                                                                   }                                                                                                
}                                                                                                   }

public boolean answerCell(boolean isMorning, boolean isMom, boolean isAsleep)                       public boolean answerCell(boolean isMorning, boolean isMom, boolean isAsleep)                       
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    if (isAsleep) {                                                                                     if (isAsleep) {                                                                                 
        return false;                                                                                       return false;                                                                               
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else if (isMorning && isMom) {                                                                      else if (isMorning && isMom) {                                                                  
        return true;                                                                                        return true;                                                                                
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else {                                                                                              else if (!isMorning) {                                                                          
        return false;                                                                                       return true;                                                                                
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
}                                                                                                       else {                                                                                          
                                                                                                            return false;                                                                               
                                                                                                        }                                                                                               
                                                                                                    }                                                                                                   
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
public boolean answerCell(boolean isMorning, boolean isMom, boolean isAsleep)                       public boolean answerCell(boolean isMorning, boolean isMom, boolean isAsleep)                       
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    if (isAsleep)                                                                                       if (isAsleep)                                                                                   
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
     	return false;                                                                                      	return false;                                                                                 
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    if (isMorning && isMom)                                                                             if (isMorning && isMom)                                                                         
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
     	return true;                                                                                       	return true;                                                                                  
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else                                                                                                else if (isMorning && !isMom)                                                                   
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
     	return false;                                                                                      	return false;                                                                                 
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
                                                                                                        return true;                                                                                    
}                                                                                                   }                                                                                                   
***********************************************************************************************************************


public int loneSum(int a, int b, int c)                                                             public int loneSum(int a, int b, int c)                                                             
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    if (a == b)                                                                                         if (a == b && b == c)                                                                           
        return (c);                                                                                         return 0;                                                                                   
    if (c == b)                                                                                         if (a == b)                                                                                     
        return (a);                                                                                         return (c);                                                                                 
    if (c == a)                                                                                         if (c == b)                                                                                     
        return (b);                                                                                         return (a);                                                                                 
    if (a == b && b == c)                                                                               if (c == a)                                                                                     
    {                                                                                                       return (b);                                                                                 
        return 0;                                                                                       return (a + b + c);                                                                             
    }                                                                                               }                                                                                                   
    return (a + b + c);                                                                                                                                                                                 
}

public int loneSum(int a, int b, int c)                                                             public int loneSum(int a, int b, int c)                                                             
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    if (a == b )                                                                                        if (a == b && b == c)                                                                           
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        return c;                                                                                           return 0;                                                                                   
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else if (b == c)                                                                                                                                                                                    
    {                                                                                                   if (a == b )                                                                                    
        return a;                                                                                       {                                                                                               
    }                                                                                                       return c;                                                                                   
    else if (a == c)                                                                                    }                                                                                               
    {                                                                                                   else if (b == c)                                                                                
        return b;                                                                                       {                                                                                               
    }                                                                                                       return a;                                                                                   
    return a + b + c;                                                                                   }                                                                                               
}                                                                                                       else if (a == c)                                                                                
                                                                                                        {                                                                                               
                                                                                                            return b;                                                                                   
                                                                                                        }                                                                                               
                                                                                                        return a + b + c;                                                                               
                                                                                                    }

public boolean answerCell(boolean isMorning, boolean isMom, boolean isAsleep)                       public boolean answerCell(boolean isMorning, boolean isMom, boolean isAsleep)                       
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    if (isAsleep)                                                                                       if (isAsleep)                                                                                   
        return false;                                                                                       return false;                                                                               
    else if (isMorning && isMom)                                                                        else if (isMorning && isMom)                                                                    
        return true;                                                                                        return true;                                                                                
    else                                                                                                else if (!isAsleep && !isMorning)                                                               
        return false;                                                                                       return true;                                                                                
}                                                                                                       else                                                                                            
                                                                                                            return false;                                                                               
                                                                                                    }                                                                                                   
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
public boolean answerCell(boolean isMorning, boolean isMom, boolean isAsleep)                       public boolean answerCell(boolean isMorning, boolean isMom, boolean isAsleep)                       
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    if (isAsleep) {                                                                                     if (isAsleep) {                                                                                 
        return false;                                                                                       return false;                                                                               
    } else if (isMorning && isMom) {                                                                    } else if (isMorning && isMom) {                                                                
        return true;                                                                                        return true;                                                                                
    } else {                                                                                            } else if (!isMorning && !isAsleep) {                                                           
        return false;                                                                                       return true;                                                                                
    }                                                                                                   } else {                                                                                        
}                                                                                                           return false;                                                                               
                                                                                                        }                                                                                               
                                                                                                                                                                                                        
                                                                                                    }

public int loneSum(int a, int b, int c)                                                             public int loneSum(int a, int b, int c)                                                             
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    if (a != b && b!= c && a != c)                                                                      if (a != b && b!= c && a != c)                                                                  
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
     	return a + b + c;                                                                                  	return a + b + c;                                                                             
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else if (a == b && c != b && c != a)                                                                else if (a == b && c != b && c != a)                                                            
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
     	return c;                                                                                          	return c;                                                                                     
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else if (b == c && a != c && a != b)                                                                else if (b == c && a != c && a != b)                                                            
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
     	return a;                                                                                          	return a;                                                                                     
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else                                                                                                else if (a == b && b == c && a == c)                                                            
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
     	return b;                                                                                          	return 0;                                                                                     
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
}                                                                                                       else                                                                                            
                                                                                                        {                                                                                               
                                                                                                         	return b;                                                                                     
                                                                                                        }                                                                                               
                                                                                                    }                                                                                                   
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
public int loneSum(int a, int b, int c)                                                             public int loneSum(int a, int b, int c)                                                             
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    if (a == b)                                                                                         if (a == b && b != c)                                                                           
        return c;                                                                                           return c;                                                                                   
    if (a == c)                                                                                         if (a == c && c != b)                                                                           
        return b;                                                                                           return b;                                                                                   
    if (b == c)                                                                                         if (b == c && c != a)                                                                           
        return a;                                                                                           return a;                                                                                   
    if (a != b && a != c && b != c)                                                                     if (a != b && a != c && b != c)                                                                 
        return a + b + c;                                                                                   return a + b + c;                                                                           
    else                                                                                                else                                                                                            
        return 0;                                                                                           return 0;                                                                                   
}                                                                                                   }

public int loneSum(int a, int b, int c)                                                             public int loneSum(int a, int b, int c)                                                             
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    int sum = a + b + c;                                                                                int sum = a + b + c;                                                                            
    if (a == b)                                                                                         if (a == b)                                                                                     
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        return b + c;                                                                                       return c;                                                                                   
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else if (b == c)                                                                                    else if (b == c)                                                                                
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        return a + b;                                                                                       return a;                                                                                   
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else if (a == c)                                                                                    else if (a == c)                                                                                
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        return b + a;                                                                                       return b;                                                                                   
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else                                                                                                else                                                                                            
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        return sum;                                                                                         return sum;                                                                                 
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
}                                                                                                   }

public int loneSum(int a, int b, int c)                                                             public int loneSum(int a, int b, int c)                                                             
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    if (a == b && b != c)                                                                               if (a == b && b != c)                                                                           
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        return c;                                                                                           return c;                                                                                   
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else if (a == c && a != b)                                                                          else if (a == c && a != b)                                                                      
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        return b;                                                                                           return b;                                                                                   
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else if (b == c && b != a)                                                                          else if (b == c && b != a)                                                                      
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        return a;                                                                                           return a;                                                                                   
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else                                                                                                else if (a == b && c == b)                                                                      
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        return a + b + c;                                                                                   return 0;                                                                                   
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
}                                                                                                       else                                                                                            
                                                                                                        {                                                                                               
                                                                                                            return a + b + c;                                                                           
                                                                                                        }                                                                                               
                                                                                                    }

    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        return a+b+c;                                                                                       return a+b+c;                                                                               
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else if (a==b)                                                                                      else if (a==b && b != c)                                                                        
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        return c;                                                                                           return c;                                                                                   
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else if (a==c)                                                                                      else if (a==c && c != b)                                                                        
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        return b;                                                                                           return b;                                                                                   
    }                                                                                                   }

{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    if ((a + b) >= 10 || (a + b) <= 19) {                                                               if ((a + b) >= 10 && (a + b) <= 19) {                                                           
        return 20;                                                                                          return 20;                                                                                  
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else return a + b;                                                                                  else return a + b;                                                                              
}                                                                                                   }

        return b + c;                                                                                       return c;                                                                                   
    else if (b == c || b == a)                                                                          else if (a == c)                                                                                
        return a + c;                                                                                       return b;                                                                                   
    else if (c == b || c == a)                                                                          else if (b == c)                                                                                
        return b + a;                                                                                       return a;                                                                                   
    else                                                                                                else                                                                                            
        return a + b + c;                                                                                   return a + b + c;                                                                           
}                                                                                                   }

public int sortaSum(int a, int b)                                                                   public int sortaSum(int a, int b)                                                                   
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    int sum = 0;                                                                                        int sum = 0;                                                                                    
    sum = a + b;                                                                                        sum = a + b;                                                                                    
    if (sum >= 10 || sum <= 19)                                                                         if (sum >= 10 && sum <= 19)                                                                     
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
     	sum = 20;                                                                                          	sum = 20;                                                                                     
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    return sum;                                                                                         return sum;                                                                                     
}                                                                                                   }

public int blackjack(int a, int b)                                                                  public int blackjack(int a, int b)                                                                  
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    if (a > 21 && b > 21)                                                                               if (a > 21 && b > 21)                                                                           
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
    return 0;                                                                                           return 0;                                                                                       
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else if ( a <= 21 && a > b )                                                                        else if ( a <= 21 && a > b || a <= 21 && b > 21 )                                               
        return a;                                                                                           return a;                                                                                   
    else if ( b <= 21 && a < b )                                                                        else if ( b <= 21 && a < b || b <= 21 && a> 21)                                                 
        return b;                                                                                           return b;                                                                                   
    return 0;                                                                                       return 0;// ???                                                                                     
}                                                                                                   }

public int blackjack(int a, int b)                                                                  public int blackjack(int a, int b)                                                                  
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    if (a > 21 || b > 21)                                                                               if (a > 21)                                                                                     
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        return 0;                                                                                           a = 0;                                                                                      
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    if (a>b)                                                                                            if (b > 21)                                                                                     
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        return a;                                                                                           b = 0;                                                                                      
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else                                                                                                if (a>b)                                                                                        
        return b;                                                                                       {                                                                                               
}                                                                                                           return a;                                                                                   
                                                                                                        }                                                                                               
                                                                                                        else                                                                                            
                                                                                                            return b;                                                                                   
                                                                                                    }

public int loneSum(int a, int b, int c)                                                             public int loneSum(int a, int b, int c)                                                             
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    if(a==b)                                                                                            if(a == c && b == c && a==b)                                                                    
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
    	return c;                                                                                          	return 0;                                                                                      
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else if(b == c)                                                                                     else if(a==b)                                                                                   
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
    	return a;                                                                                          	return c;                                                                                      
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else if(a == c)                                                                                     else if(b == c)                                                                                 
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
    	return b;                                                                                          	return a;                                                                                      
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else if(a == c && b == c && a==b)                                                                   else if(a == c)                                                                                 
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
    	return 0;                                                                                          	return b;                                                                                      
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    return (a + b + c);                                                                                 return (a + b + c);                                                                             
}                                                                                                   }

public int loneSum(int a, int b, int c)                                                             public int loneSum(int a, int b, int c)                                                             
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    if (a == b)                                                                                         if (a == b && b == c)                                                                           
        return c;                                                                                           return 0;                                                                                   
    else if (b == c)                                                                                    else if (a == b)                                                                                
        return a;                                                                                           return c;                                                                                   
    else if (a == c)                                                                                    else if (b == c)                                                                                
        return b;                                                                                           return a;                                                                                   
    else if (a == b && b == c)                                                                          else if (a == c)                                                                                
        return 0;                                                                                           return b;                                                                                   
    else                                                                                                else                                                                                            
        return a + b + c;                                                                                   return a + b + c;                                                                           
}                                                                                                   }
