public int loneSum(int a, int b, int c)                                                             public int loneSum(int a, int b, int c)                                                             
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    if (a != b && b != c && a != c)                                                                     if (a != b && b != c && a != c)                                                                 
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        return a+b+c;                                                                                       return a+b+c;                                                                               
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else if (a==b)                                                                                      else if (a==b && b != c)                                                                        
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        return c;                                                                                           return c;                                                                                   
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else if (a==c)                                                                                      else if (a==c && c != b)                                                                        
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        return b;                                                                                           return b;                                                                                   
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else if (a==b && b== c && a==c)                                                                     else if (a==b && b== c && a==c)                                                                 
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        return a;                                                                                           return 0;                                                                                   
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else                                                                                                else                                                                                            
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        return a;                                                                                           return a;                                                                                   
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
                                                                                                                                                                                                        
}                                                                                                   }                                                                                                   
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
public int loneSum(int a, int b, int c)                                                             public int loneSum(int a, int b, int c)                                                             
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    if (a == b)                                                                                         if (a == b && b != c)                                                                           
        return c;                                                                                           return c;                                                                                   
    if (a == c)                                                                                         if (a == c && c != b)                                                                           
        return b;                                                                                           return b;                                                                                   
    if (b == c)                                                                                         if (b == c && c != a)                                                                           
        return a;                                                                                           return a;                                                                                   
    if (a != b && a != c && b != c)                                                                     if (a != b && a != c && b != c)                                                                 
        return a + b + c;                                                                                   return a + b + c;                                                                           
    else                                                                                                else                                                                                            
        return 0;                                                                                           return 0;                                                                                   
}                                                                                                   }

public boolean isEverywhere(int[] nums, int val)                                                    public boolean isEverywhere(int[] nums, int val)                                                    
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    int length = nums.length;                                                                           int length = nums.length;                                                                       
    for (int i = 0; i < length; i ++){                                                                  for (int i = 0; i < length - 1; i ++){                                                          
        if (nums[i] == val || nums[i + 1] == val){                                                          if (nums[i] == val || nums[i + 1] == val){                                                  
            continue;                                                                                           continue;                                                                               
        }                                                                                                   }                                                                                           
        else{                                                                                               else{                                                                                       
            return false;                                                                                       return false;                                                                           
        }                                                                                                   }                                                                                           
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    return true;                                                                                        return true;                                                                                    
}                                                                                                   }

     int total = 0;                                                                                      int total = 0;                                                                                 
   for(int i = 0; i < nums.length; i++)                                                                for(int i = 0; i < nums.length - 1; i++)                                                         
   {                                                                                                   {                                                                                                
   		if( nums[i] == val || nums[i + 1] == val)                                                         		if( nums[i] == val || nums[i + 1] == val)                                                      
   			{                                                                                                			{                                                                                             
  			total = total + 1;                                                                               			total = total + 1;                                                                             
  			 }                                                                                               			 }                                                                                             
  		 else                                                                                             		 else                                                                                           
			{                                                                                                			{                                                                                                
       return false;                                                                                       return false;                                                                                
  			 }                                                                                               			 }                                                                                             
   }                                                                                                   }                                                                                                
    return true;                                                                                        return true;                                                                                    
}                                                                                                   }

public int loneSum(int a, int b, int c)                                                             public int loneSum(int a, int b, int c)                                                             
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    if(a == b)                                                                                          if (a == b && b == c)                                                                           
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        a = 0;                                                                                              a = 0;                                                                                      
        b = 0;                                                                                              b = 0;                                                                                      
    }                                                                                                       c = 0;                                                                                      
    if(b == c)                                                                                          }                                                                                               
    {                                                                                                   if(a == b)                                                                                      
        b = 0;                                                                                          {                                                                                               
        c = 0;                                                                                              a = 0;                                                                                      
    }                                                                                                       b = 0;                                                                                      
    if (a == c)                                                                                         }                                                                                               
    {                                                                                                   if(b == c)                                                                                      
        a = 0;                                                                                          {                                                                                               
        c = 0;                                                                                              b = 0;                                                                                      
    }                                                                                                       c = 0;                                                                                      
    if (a == b && b == c)                                                                               }                                                                                               
    {                                                                                                   if (a == c)                                                                                     
        a = 0;                                                                                          {                                                                                               
        b = 0;                                                                                              a = 0;                                                                                      
        c = 0;                                                                                              c = 0;                                                                                      
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    int sum = a + b + c;                                                                                int sum = a + b + c;                                                                            
    return sum;                                                                                         return sum;                                                                                     
}                                                                                                   }

        a = 0;                                                                                          	if(a == c)                                                                                     
        b = 0;                                                                                              {                                                                                           
    }                                                                                                   	    return 0;                                                                                  
    if (b == c)                                                                                             }

        c = 0;                                                                                        	if(a == c)

    if (a == c)                                                                                         	return b;                                                                                      
    {                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
        a = 0;                                                                                        	if(b == c)

    }                                                                                                   	return a;

        a = 0;                                                                                      }                                                                                                   
        b = 0;                                                                                                                                                                                          
        c = 0;                                                                                                                                                                                          
    }

public boolean answerCell(boolean isMorning, boolean isMom, boolean isAsleep)                       public boolean answerCell(boolean isMorning, boolean isMom, boolean isAsleep)                       
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    boolean t=true;                                                                                     boolean t=true;                                                                                 
    if (isMorning==true && isMom==true)                                                                 if (isAsleep==true)                                                                             
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        t=true;                                                                                             t=false;                                                                                    
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else if (isAsleep==true)                                                                            else if (isMorning==true && isMom==true)                                                        
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        t=false;                                                                                            t=true;                                                                                     
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else if (isMorning==true && isMom!=true)                                                                                                                                                            
    {                                                                                                   else if (isMorning==true && isMom!=true)                                                        
        t=false;                                                                                        {                                                                                               
    }                                                                                                       t=false;                                                                                    
                                                                                                        }                                                                                               
    else                                                                                                                                                                                                
    {                                                                                                   else                                                                                            
    	t=true;                                                                                            {                                                                                               
    }                                                                                                   	t=true;                                                                                        
    return t;                                                                                           }                                                                                               
}                                                                                                       return t;                                                                                       
                                                                                                    }

public boolean answerCell(boolean isMorning, boolean isMom, boolean isAsleep)                       public boolean answerCell(boolean isMorning, boolean isMom, boolean isAsleep)                       
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    if (isMorning&&isMom)                                                                               if (isMorning&&isMom&&!isAsleep)                                                                
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        return true;                                                                                        return true;                                                                                
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else if (isMorning||isAsleep)                                                                       else if (isMorning||isAsleep)                                                                   
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        return false;                                                                                       return false;                                                                               
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else                                                                                                else                                                                                            
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        return true;                                                                                        return true;                                                                                
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
}                                                                                                   }

    if (a != b && b != c && c!= a)                                                                      if (a != b && b != c && c!= a)                                                                  
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        return sum;                                                                                         return sum;                                                                                 
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
                                                                                                                                                                                                        
    else if (a == b)                                                                                    else if (a == b && b == c)                                                                      
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        return c;                                                                                           return 0;                                                                                   
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
                                                                                                                                                                                                        
    else if (a == c)                                                                                    else if (a == b)                                                                                
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        return b;                                                                                           return c;                                                                                   
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
                                                                                                                                                                                                        
    else if (b == c)                                                                                    else if (a == c)                                                                                
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        return a ;                                                                                          return b;                                                                                   
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
                                                                                                                                                                                                        
    else                                                                                                else                                                                                            
    {                                                                                                   {

    }                                                                                                   }

    }                                                                                                   }

        return a;                                                                                           return a;                                                                                   
    }                                                                                                   }

    }                                                                                                   }

        {                                                                                                   {

        }                                                                                                   }                                                                                           
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    return true;                                                                                        return true;

public int loneSum(int a, int b, int c)                                                             public int loneSum(int a, int b, int c)                                                             
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    if (a == b)                                                                                         if (a == b && b == c)                                                                           
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        return c;                                                                                           return 0;                                                                                   
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else if (a == c)                                                                                    else if (a == b)                                                                                
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        return b;                                                                                           return c;                                                                                   
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else if (b == c)                                                                                    else if (a == c)                                                                                
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        return a;                                                                                           return b;                                                                                   
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else if (a == b && b == c)                                                                          else if (b == c)                                                                                
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        return 0;                                                                                           return a;                                                                                   
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else                                                                                                else                                                                                            
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        return a + b + c;                                                                                   return a + b + c;                                                                           
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
}                                                                                                   }

public int loneSum(int a, int b, int c)                                                             public int loneSum(int a, int b, int c)                                                             
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    if (a == b)                                                                                         if (a == b && b == c)                                                                           
        return c;                                                                                           return 0;                                                                                   
    else if (b == c)                                                                                    else if (a == b)                                                                                
        return a;                                                                                           return c;                                                                                   
    else if (a == c)                                                                                    else if (b == c)                                                                                
        return b;                                                                                           return a;                                                                                   
    else if (a == b && b == c)                                                                          else if (a == c)                                                                                
        return 0;                                                                                           return b;                                                                                   
    else                                                                                                else                                                                                            
        return a + b + c;                                                                                   return a + b + c;                                                                           
}                                                                                                   }

public String zipZap(String str)                                                                    public String zipZap(String str)                                                                    
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    String s = "";                                                                                      String s = "";                                                                                  
    int x = 0;                                                                                          int x = 0;                                                                                      
    int y = 0;                                                                                          int y = 0;                                                                                      
    if (str.length() < 3) {                                                                             if (str.length() < 3) {                                                                         
        return str;                                                                                         return str;                                                                                 
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else {                                                                                              else {                                                                                          
        for (int i = 0; i < str.length() - 2; i++) {                                                        for (int i = 0; i < str.length() - 2; i++) {                                                
            if (str.charAt(i) == 'z' && str.charAt(i + 2) == 'p') {                                             if (str.charAt(i) == 'z' && str.charAt(i + 2) == 'p') {                                 
                x++;                                                                                                x++;                                                                                
            }                                                                                                   }                                                                                       
        }                                                                                                   }                                                                                           
    	while (s.length() != str.length() - x && y <= str.length()) {                                      	while (s.length() != str.length() - x && y <= str.length() - 2) {                              
            if (str.charAt(y) == 'z' && str.charAt(y + 2) == 'p') {                                             if (str.charAt(y) == 'z' && str.charAt(y + 2) == 'p') {                                 
                s = s + "zp";                                                                                       s = s + "zp";                                                                       
                y++;                                                                                                y++;                                                                                
            }                                                                                                   }                                                                                       
            else {                                                                                              else {                                                                                  
                s = s + str.charAt(y);                                                                              s = s + str.charAt(y);                                                              
            }                                                                                                   }                                                                                       
            y++;                                                                                                y++;                                                                                    
        }                                                                                                   }                                                                                           
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    return s;                                                                                           return s;                                                                                       
                                                                                                                                                                                                        
                                                                                                                                                                                                        
}                                                                                                   }

public int luckySum(int a, int b, int c)                                                            public int luckySum(int a, int b, int c)                                                            
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    int s1=a+b+c;                                                                                       int s1=a+b+c;                                                                                   
    int s2=a+b;                                                                                         int s2=a+b;                                                                                     
    int s3=a;                                                                                           int s3=a;                                                                                       
    int s=0;                                                                                            int s=0;                                                                                        
    if ((b==13 && c==13) || b==13)                                                                      if (a==13)                                                                                      
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        s=s3;                                                                                               s=0;                                                                                        
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else if (c==13)                                                                                     else if ((b==13 && c==13) || b==13)                                                             
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        s=s2;                                                                                               s=s3;                                                                                       
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else                                                                                                else if (c==13)                                                                                 
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        s=s1;                                                                                               s=s2;                                                                                       
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    return s;                                                                                           else                                                                                            
}                                                                                                       {                                                                                               
                                                                                                            s=s1;                                                                                       
                                                                                                        }                                                                                               
                                                                                                        return s;                                                                                       
                                                                                                    }

public boolean answerCell(boolean isMorning, boolean isMom, boolean isAsleep)                       public boolean answerCell(boolean isMorning, boolean isMom, boolean isAsleep)                       
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
	if (isMorning && isMom)                                                                            	if (isMorning && isMom && !isAsleep)                                                               
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        return true;                                                                                        return true;                                                                                
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else if (!isMorning && !isAsleep)                                                                   else if (!isAsleep && !isMorning)                                                               
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        return true;                                                                                		return true;                                                                                      
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    return false;                                                                                       return false;                                                                                   
}                                                                                                   }

public int blackjack(int a, int b)                                                                  public int blackjack(int a, int b)                                                                  
{ assert(a > 0);                                                                                    { assert(a > 0);                                                                                    
 assert(b>0);                                                                                        assert(b>0);                                                                                       
    if ((a > 21) && (b > 21)) {                                                                         if ((a > 21) && (b > 21)) {                                                                     
        return 0;                                                                                           return 0;                                                                                   
    }                                                                                                   } else if (a > 21) {                                                                            
 int difference_a_21 = 21 - a;                                                                              return b;

 if (difference_a_21 > difference_b_21) {                                                                   return a;

 } else {                                                                                            int difference_a_21 = 21 - a;                                                                      
     return a;                                                                                       int difference_b_21 = 21 - b;                                                                      
 }                                                                                                   if (difference_a_21 > difference_b_21) {

                                                                                                     }                                                                                                  
                                                                                                    }

public int blackjack(int a, int b)                                                                  public int blackjack(int a, int b)                                                                  
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
   if (21-a < 0 && 21-b < 0) {                                                                         if (21-a < 0 && 21-b < 0) {                                                                      
       return 0;                                                                                           return 0;                                                                                    
   }                                                                                                   }                                                                                                
    else if (21-a < 21-b) {                                                                             else if (21-a <0 && 21-b>0) {                                                                   
        return a;                                                                                           return b;                                                                                   
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else {                                                                                              else if (21-b <0 && 21-a > 0) {                                                                 
        return b;                                                                                           return a;                                                                                   
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
}                                                                                                       else if (21-a < 21-b) {                                                                         
                                                                                                            return a;                                                                                   
                                                                                                        }                                                                                               
                                                                                                        else {                                                                                          
                                                                                                            return b;                                                                                   
                                                                                                        }                                                                                               
                                                                                                    }

public int sortaSum(int a, int b)                                                                   public int sortaSum(int a, int b)

    if (sum >= 10 || sum <= 19)                                                                         if (sum >= 10 && sum <= 19)                                                                     
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        sum = 20;                                                                                           sum = 20;                                                                                   
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
                                                                                                                                                                                                        
    return sum;                                                                                         return sum;                                                                                     
                                                                                                                                                                                                        
}                                                                                                   }

public int loneSum(int a, int b, int c)                                                             public int loneSum(int a, int b, int c)                                                             
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    int sum = 0;                                                                                        int sum = 0;                                                                                    
                                                                                                                                                                                                        
    if (a == b)                                                                                         if (a == b && b == c)                                                                           
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        sum = c;                                                                                            sum = 0;                                                                                    
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else if (a == c)                                                                                    else if (a == b)                                                                                
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        sum = b;                                                                                            sum = c;                                                                                    
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else if (b == c)                                                                                    else if (a == c)                                                                                
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        sum = a;                                                                                            sum = b;                                                                                    
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else                                                                                                else if (b == c)                                                                                
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        sum = a + b + c;                                                                                    sum = a;                                                                                    
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
                                                                                                        else                                                                                            
    return sum;                                                                                         {                                                                                               
}                                                                                                           sum = a + b + c;                                                                            
                                                                                                        }                                                                                               
                                                                                                                                                                                                        
                                                                                                        return sum;                                                                                     
                                                                                                    }

public int loneSum(int a, int b, int c)                                                             public int loneSum(int a, int b, int c)                                                             
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
	if (a == b)                                                                                            if (a == b && b == c)                                                                           
        return c;                                                                                           return 0;                                                                                   
    else if (a == c)                                                                                	else if (a == b)                                                                                   
        return b;                                                                                           return c;                                                                                   
    else if (b == c)                                                                                    else if (a == c)                                                                                
        return a;                                                                                           return b;                                                                                   
    else                                                                                                else if (b == c)                                                                                
        return a + b + c;                                                                                   return a;                                                                                   
}                                                                                                       else                                                                                            
                                                                                                            return a + b + c;                                                                           
                                                                                                    }

    if (a==b)                                                                                           if (a==b && b==c)                                                                               
        output =  c;                                                                                        output =  0;                                                                                
    else if (b==c)                                                                                      else if (b==c)                                                                                  
        output = a;                                                                                         output = a;                                                                                 
    else if (a==c)                                                                                      else if (a==c)                                                                                  
        output = b;                                                                                         output = b;                                                                                 
    else if (a==b && b==c)                                                                              else if (a==b)                                                                                  
        output = 0;                                                                                         output = c;                                                                                 
    else                                                                                                else                                                                                            
        output = a+b+c;                                                                                     output = a+b+c;                                                                             
    return output;                                                                                      return output;                                                                                  
}                                                                                                   }

        return c;                                                                                           return c;

    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
}                                                                                                   }

public int loneSum(int a, int b, int c)                                                             public int loneSum(int a, int b, int c)                                                             
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    if (a != b && b != c && a != c)                                                                     if (a != b && b != c && a != c)                                                                 
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        return a + b + c;                                                                                   return a + b + c;                                                                           
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else if (a == b)                                                                                    else if (a == b && b == c && c == a)                                                            
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        return c;                                                                                           return 0;                                                                                   
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else if (a == c)                                                                                    else if (a == b)                                                                                
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        return b;                                                                                           return c;                                                                                   
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else if (b == c)                                                                                    else if (a == c)                                                                                
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        return a;                                                                                           return b;                                                                                   
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else                                                                                                else                                                                                            
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        return 0;                                                                                           return a;                                                                                   
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
}                                                                                                   }
