public int loneSum(int a, int b, int c)                                                             public int loneSum(int a, int b, int c)                                                             
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    if (a == b)                                                                                         if (a == b && b != c)                                                                           
        return c;                                                                                           return c;                                                                                   
    if (a == c)                                                                                         if (a == c && c != b)                                                                           
        return b;                                                                                           return b;                                                                                   
    if (b == c)                                                                                         if (b == c && c != a)                                                                           
        return a;                                                                                           return a;                                                                                   
    if (a != b && a != c && b != c)                                                                     if (a != b && a != c && b != c)                                                                 
        return a + b + c;                                                                                   return a + b + c;                                                                           
    else                                                                                                else                                                                                            
        return 0;                                                                                           return 0;                                                                                   
}                                                                                                   }

public boolean isEverywhere(int[] nums, int val)                                                    public boolean isEverywhere(int[] nums, int val)                                                    
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    for (int i = 0 ; nums.length > i; i++)                                                              for (int i = 0 ; nums.length -1 > i; i++)                                                       
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        if (nums[i] != val && nums[i+1] != val)                                                             if (nums[i] != val && nums[i+1] != val)                                                     
        {                                                                                                   {                                                                                           
            return false;                                                                                       return false;                                                                           
        }                                                                                                   }                                                                                           
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    return true;                                                                                        return true;                                                                                    
                                                                                                                                                                                                        
}                                                                                                   }                                                                                                   
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
public boolean isEverywhere(int[] nums, int val)                                                    public boolean isEverywhere(int[] nums, int val)                                                    
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    for (int i = 0; i < nums.length; i++)                                                               for (int i = 0; i < nums.length -1; i++)                                                        
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        if (nums[i] != val && nums[i+1] != val)                                                             if (nums[i] != val && nums[i+1] != val)                                                     
        {                                                                                                   {                                                                                           
            return false;                                                                                       return false;                                                                           
        }                                                                                                   }                                                                                           
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    return true;                                                                                        return true;                                                                                    
}                                                                                                   }

        return a;                                                                                           return c;                                                                                   
    else if (a == c)                                                                                    else if (b == c)                                                                                
        return b;                                                                                           return a;                                                                                   
    else if (a == b && b == c)                                                                          else if (a == c)                                                                                
        return 0;                                                                                           return b;                                                                                   
    else                                                                                                else                                                                                            
        return a + b + c;                                                                                   return a + b + c;                                                                           
}                                                                                                   }

        return b;                                                                                       {

    if (a == b)                                                                                         return c;                                                                                       
        return c;                                                                                       }                                                                                               
    if (a == b && b == c)                                                                               if (a == c)                                                                                     
        return 0;                                                                                           return b;                                                                                   
    return (a+b+c);                                                                                     if (b == c)                                                                                     
}                                                                                                           return a;                                                                                   
                                                                                                        return (a+b+c);                                                                                 
                                                                                                    }

public int loneSum(int a, int b, int c)                                                             public int loneSum(int a, int b, int c)                                                             
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    int sum;                                                                                            int sum;                                                                                        
    if (a==b)                                                                                           if (a==b && a==c)                                                                               
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
 		sum = c;    	                                                                                         	sum = 0;                                                                                      
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else if (a==c)                                                                                      else if (a==b)                                                                                  
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
     	sum = b;                                                                                       		sum = c;    	                                                                                    
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else if (b==c)                                                                                      else if (a==c)                                                                                  
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
     	sum = a;                                                                                           	sum = b;                                                                                      
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else if (a==b && a==c)                                                                              else if (b==c)                                                                                  
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
     	sum = 0;                                                                                           	sum = a;                                                                                      
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else                                                                                                else                                                                                            
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
     	sum = a + b + c;                                                                                   	sum = a + b + c;                                                                              
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    return sum;                                                                                         return sum;                                                                                     
}                                                                                                   }

public int loneSum(int a, int b, int c)                                                             public int loneSum(int a, int b, int c)                                                             
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    if (a!=b&&a!=c&&b!=c)                                                                               if (a!=b&&a!=c&&b!=c)                                                                           
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        return (a+b+c);                                                                                     return (a+b+c);                                                                             
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else if (a==b)                                                                                      else if (a==b&&b==c)                                                                            
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        return c;                                                                                           return 0;                                                                                   
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else if (b==c)                                                                                      else if (a==b)                                                                                  
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        return a;                                                                                           return c;                                                                                   
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else if (a==c)                                                                                      else if (b==c)                                                                                  
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        return b;                                                                                           return a;                                                                                   
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else                                                                                                else if (a==c)                                                                                  
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        return 0;                                                                                           return b;                                                                                   
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
                                                                                                        else                                                                                            
}                                                                                                       {                                                                                               
                                                                                                            return 0;                                                                                   
                                                                                                        }                                                                                               
                                                                                                                                                                                                        
                                                                                                    }

public int loneSum(int a, int b, int c)                                                             public int loneSum(int a, int b, int c)                                                             
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
   if (a == b && b!=c) {                                                                               if (a == b && b == c) {                                                                          
       return c;                                                                                           return 0;                                                                                    
   }                                                                                                   }                                                                                                
    else if (a==c && b!=c) {                                                                            if (a == b && b!=c) {                                                                           
        return b;                                                                                          return c;                                                                                    
    }                                                                                                  }                                                                                                
    else if (b == c && a!=b) {                                                                          else if (a==c && b!=c) {                                                                        
        return a;                                                                                           return b;                                                                                   
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else {                                                                                              else if (b == c && a!=b) {                                                                      
        return a+b+c;                                                                                       return a;                                                                                   
	}                                                                                                      }                                                                                               
}                                                                                                       else {                                                                                          
                                                                                                            return a+b+c;                                                                               
                                                                                                    	}                                                                                                  
                                                                                                    }

public int loneSum(int a, int b, int c)                                                             public int loneSum(int a, int b, int c)                                                             
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    if (a == b)                                                                                         if (a == b && b != c)                                                                           
        return c;                                                                                           return c;                                                                                   
    if (a == c)                                                                                         if (a == c && c != b)                                                                           
        return b;                                                                                           return b;                                                                                   
    if (b == c)                                                                                         if (b == c && c != a)                                                                           
        return a;                                                                                           return a;                                                                                   
    if (a == b && b == c)                                                                               if (a == b && b == c)                                                                           
        return 0;                                                                                           return 0;                                                                                   
    else                                                                                                else                                                                                            
        return a + b + c;                                                                                   return a + b + c;                                                                           
}                                                                                                   }

public int loneSum(int a, int b, int c)                                                             public int loneSum(int a, int b, int c)                                                             
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    if (a == b) {                                                                                       if (a == b && b == c && a == c) {                                                               
        return c;                                                                                           return 0;                                                                                   
    } else if (b == c) {                                                                                } else if (a == b) {                                                                            
        return a;                                                                                           return c;                                                                                   
    } else if (a == c) {                                                                                } else if (b == c) {                                                                            
        return b;                                                                                           return a;                                                                                   
    } else if (a == b && b == c && a == c) {                                                            } else if (a == c) {                                                                            
        return 0;                                                                                           return b;                                                                                   
    } else {                                                                                            } else {                                                                                        
        return a + b + c;                                                                                   return a + b + c;                                                                           
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
}                                                                                                   }

public int loneSum(int a, int b, int c)                                                             public int loneSum(int a, int b, int c)                                                             
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    if ((a == b) && (b == c))                                                                           if ((a == b) && (b == c))                                                                       
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        return a;                                                                                           return 0;                                                                                   
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else if (a == b)                                                                                    else if (a == b)                                                                                
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        return c;                                                                                           return c;                                                                                   
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else if (b == c)                                                                                    else if (b == c)                                                                                
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        return a;                                                                                           return a;                                                                                   
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else if (a == c)                                                                                    else if (a == c)                                                                                
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        return b;                                                                                           return b;                                                                                   
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else                                                                                                else                                                                                            
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        return a + b + c;                                                                                   return a + b + c;                                                                           
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
}                                                                                                   }

{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    if (a == b)                                                                                         if (a == b && b == c)                                                                           
        return c;                                                                                           return 0;                                                                                   
    if (b == c)                                                                                         if (a == b)                                                                                     
        return a;                                                                                           return c;                                                                                   
    if (a == c)                                                                                         if (b == c)                                                                                     
        return b;                                                                                           return a;                                                                                   
    return a + b + c;                                                                                   if (a == c)                                                                                     
}                                                                                                           return b;                                                                                   
                                                                                                        return a + b + c;                                                                               
                                                                                                    }

public int loneSum(int a, int b, int c)                                                             public int loneSum(int a, int b, int c)                                                             
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    if (a == b) {                                                                                       if (a == b && b == c && a == c) {                                                               
        return c;                                                                                           return 0;                                                                                   
    } else if (b == c) {                                                                                } else if (a == b) {                                                                            
        return a;                                                                                           return c;                                                                                   
    } else if (a == c) {                                                                                } else if (b == c) {                                                                            
        return b;                                                                                           return a;                                                                                   
    } else if (a == b && b == c && a == c) {                                                            } else if (a == c) {                                                                            
        return 0;                                                                                           return b;                                                                                   
    } else {                                                                                            } else {                                                                                        
        return a + b + c;                                                                                   return a + b + c;                                                                           
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
}                                                                                                   }                                                                                                   
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
public int loneSum(int a, int b, int c)                                                             public int loneSum(int a, int b, int c)                                                             
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    if (a == b)                                                                                         if (a == b && b == c)                                                                           
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        return c;                                                                                           return 0;                                                                                   
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
                                                                                                                                                                                                        
    if (a == c)                                                                                         if (a == b)                                                                                     
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        return b;                                                                                           return c;                                                                                   
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
                                                                                                                                                                                                        
    if (b == c)                                                                                         if (a == c)                                                                                     
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        return a;                                                                                           return b;                                                                                   
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
                                                                                                                                                                                                        
    if (a == b && b == c)                                                                               if (b == c)                                                                                     
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        return 0;                                                                                           return a;                                                                                   
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
                                                                                                                                                                                                        
    return (a + b + c);                                                                                 return (a + b + c);                                                                             
}                                                                                                   }                                                                                                   
***********************************************************************************************************************


public int sortaSum(int a, int b)                                                                   public int sortaSum(int a, int b)                                                                   
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    int sum = a + b;                                                                                    int sum = a + b;                                                                                
    int forbidden = 20;                                                                                 int forbidden = 20;                                                                             
                                                                                                                                                                                                        
    if (sum >= 10 || sum <= 19)                                                                         if (sum >= 10 && sum <= 19)                                                                     
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        return forbidden;                                                                                   return forbidden;                                                                           
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else                                                                                                else                                                                                            
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        return sum;                                                                                         return sum;                                                                                 
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
}                                                                                                   }                                                                                                   
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
public int sortaSum(int a, int b)                                                                   public int sortaSum(int a, int b)                                                                   
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    int sum = a + b;                                                                                    int sum = a + b;                                                                                
    if(sum >= 10 || sum <= 19)                                                                          if(sum >= 10 && sum <= 19)                                                                      
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
    	return 20;                                                                                         	return 20;                                                                                     
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
                                                                                                                                                                                                        
    else                                                                                                else                                                                                            
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
    	return sum;                                                                                        	return sum;                                                                                    
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
}                                                                                                   }

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
public int loneSum(int a, int b, int c)                                                             public int loneSum(int a, int b, int c)                                                             
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    if (a == b)                                                                                         if (a == b && b == c)                                                                           
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        return c;                                                                                           return 0;                                                                                   
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
                                                                                                                                                                                                        
    if (a == c)                                                                                         if (a == b)                                                                                     
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        return b;                                                                                           return c;                                                                                   
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
                                                                                                                                                                                                        
    if (b == c)                                                                                         if (a == c)                                                                                     
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        return a;                                                                                           return b;                                                                                   
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
                                                                                                                                                                                                        
    if (a == b && b == c)                                                                               if (b == c)                                                                                     
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        return 0;                                                                                           return a;                                                                                   
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
                                                                                                                                                                                                        
    return (a + b + c);                                                                                 return (a + b + c);                                                                             
}                                                                                                   }
